com.sailthru.mobile.sdk.model

Class AttributeMap

  • com.sailthru.mobile.sdk.model.AttributeMap

  • public class AttributeMap

    A map containing the attributes to set on a device.

    • Field Detail

      • RULE_UPDATE

        public static int RULE_UPDATE

        Merge the attributes contained in this map with the existing attributes on this device.

        See Also:
        AttributeMap.setMergeRules, Constant Field Values

      • RULE_REPLACE

        public static int RULE_REPLACE

        Replace all attributes on this device with the attributes contained in this map. This will erase all pre-existing attributes.

        See Also:
        AttributeMap.setMergeRules, Constant Field Values

      • Companion

        public static com.sailthru.mobile.sdk.model.AttributeMap.Companion Companion

      • AttributeMap

        public AttributeMap(@Nullable
                    org.json.JSONObject jsonAttributes)

        Constructs a new map containing the values described in a JSONObject. Only Number, String, Boolean, and Array types are supported. null values, nested arrays, and unsupported data types will be ignored.

        Parameters:
        jsonAttributes - a JSON Object containing attributes to populate the map with
